### Gate provider

`gate.provider` controls gate-approval auth: `prompt` (chat-based, default), `auto`
(PAL if installed, else `prompt`). PAL (hardware-authenticated gates) is on the roadmap;
use `prompt` for all current workflows.

### Role registry

Role instructions live in `.claude/agents/`; config is in the `forge.roles` block above.
Pipeline: spec-author (`/spec`) → devils-advocate (read-only, before code) →
implementer (after DA, scoped writes, worktree) → validator (`/close`, read-only,
independent). Absent `.claude/agents/` → roles skipped silently.

```yaml
